---
title: Hybrid Dependencies Analysis - Main Flow
---

sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Auth as 认证模块
    participant Project as 项目管理
    participant Parser as 解析引擎
    participant Analyzer as 分析引擎
    participant Report as 报告服务
    participant DB as Database
    participant FS as File System

    Note over User,FS: 1. 注册 / 登录
    User->>Auth: POST /user/register
    Auth->>DB: 保存用户
    DB-->>Auth: OK
    Auth-->>User: Result.success()
    User->>Auth: GET /user/login
    Auth->>DB: 验证用户
    DB-->>Auth: UserDAO
    Auth-->>User: JWT Token

    Note over User,FS: 2. 上传项目
    User->>Project: POST /sourceFolder/upload (ZIP)
    Project->>Project: 解压 ZIP
    Project->>DB: 保存文件夹信息
    DB-->>Project: sourceFolderId
    Project-->>User: Result.success(sourceFolderId)

    Note over User,FS: 3. 源码解析
    User->>Parser: POST /parse/parseAll?sourceFolderId=1
    Parser->>FS: 遍历项目目录
    par Java 解析
        Parser->>Parser: Spoon 解析 .java 文件
        Parser->>Parser: 提取类、字段、方法、注解、import
        Parser->>FS: 写入 java-parse-output.json
        Parser->>DB: 保存解析记录
    and JSP 解析
        Parser->>Parser: Jasper/正则解析 .jsp 文件
        Parser->>FS: 写入 jsp-parse-output.json
        Parser->>DB: 保存解析记录
    and JSF 解析
        Parser->>Parser: Jsoup 解析 .xhtml 文件
        Parser->>FS: 写入 jsf-parse-output.json
        Parser->>DB: 保存解析记录
    and XML 解析
        Parser->>Parser: 解析 web.xml / persistence.xml / ejb-jar.xml / faces-config.xml / pom.xml
        Parser->>FS: 写入各 XML 解析 JSON
        Parser->>DB: 保存解析记录
    end
    Parser-->>User: Result.success()

    Note over User,FS: 4. 静态分析
    User->>Analyzer: POST /StaticAnalysis/annotationAnalysis
    Analyzer->>FS: 读取 java-parse-output.json
    Analyzer->>Analyzer: 统计注解使用频率
    Analyzer->>Analyzer: 生成迁移建议
    Analyzer->>FS: 写入 annotation-statistics.json
    Analyzer->>DB: 保存分析结果 (insertResult / updateResult)
    DB-->>Analyzer: OK
    Analyzer-->>User: Result.success(report)
    Note over User,FS: 其他分析同理:<br>WebXml/FileStore/Persistence/EJB/POM/FacesConfig

    Note over User,FS: 5. 查看报告
    User->>Report: GET /reports/AnnotationReport
    Report->>DB: 查询分析路径 (getAnnotationReport)
    DB-->>Report: AnalysisReportDAO (含 path)
    Report->>FS: 读取报告 JSON 文件
    FS-->>Report: 报告内容
    Report-->>User: Result.success(reportData)
    Note over User,FS: 其他报告同理:<br>WebXmlReport/FileStoreReport/PersistenceReport<br>/EjbJarReport/PomXmlReport/FacesConfigReport
